          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/-2223-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster </strong>for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once the <strong>ciabatta</strong> is warmed through, remove from the toaster and spread with a thin layer of <strong>butter</strong></p>",
