    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and pepper has caramelised, add the <strong>sliced steak</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and cook, covered, for 2-3 min further or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>Philly-style cheesesteak filling</strong></p>",
