    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> in the reserved potato pot and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>cooled potatoes</strong> and crush them lightly with a fork</p><p>Add most of the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> (save some for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> potato salad</strong></p>",
