    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stuff your <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>Philly-style cheesesteak filling</strong> and slice in half – this is your <strong>Philly-style cheesesteak sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve with the<strong> potato salad </strong>to the side and garnish with the<strong> remaining sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
